This project's license is not yet finalized. The working intent is a
source-available license with eventual conversion to an OSI-approved
license (FSL-1.1-Apache-2.0 or similar), permitting:

  * unrestricted self-hosting for personal and internal-business use
  * forking and modification for those purposes
  * contributions back to this repository

and restricting:

  * offering GitFlare as a hosted commercial service to third parties

Until a final license file replaces this placeholder, all rights are
reserved. Open an issue if you want to use this code in a way the
working intent doesn't cover and we'll figure it out.
